GOVT. DEGREE COLLEGE KOTRANKA (RAJOURI) 
Email Id: gdckotranka@gmail.com
CELEBRATES 
 
6th INTERNATIONAL YOGA DAY 
( 21 – 06 – 2020 ) 
THROUGH 
INTRA- COLLEGE INTER -COLLEGE 
• Participation of college faculty, students 
and families in practicing Yog Asana on 
21st June, 2020 
• Participation in Essay Writing Contest by 
the students of this college on “Yoga -
the Key to Wellness”. The students are 
required to send their essay of up to 500 
words in English Language up to 20th
June 2020 on college Email Id: 
(gdckotranka@gmail.com)
• Participation in the contest on 
Anulom-Vilom Pranayama/any 
yog aasana by the students of 
Degree Colleges of J&K through 
a recorded video of 35 - 45
seconds’ duration up to 21
st
June, 2020. 
• Link for registration:
https://forms.gle/q2NcvwMkZYLcgCPF9
• Link to submit video: 
https://forms.gle/wgtxEBnyp2uVih4j6
• WhatsApp No: 9821165604
• Merit E-Certificate shall be presented to 3 toppers and participation E-Certificate shall be 
given to the remaining contestants.
 
“PRACTICING YOGA: PERFECTING LIFE” 
Organizing Committee Patron
• Dr Mohd Mushtaq (Coordinator) Dr. P. BAMBROO
• Mr Ather Mehmood (Member) Principal
• Miss Rubia Kouser (Member) GDC Kotranka
